      },
      "rationale": "Analytical solutions for elastic bending of a uniform cylindrical rod were used to verify the FEA implementation. Deviations of <0.5% were observed for stiffness and force predictions, confirming correct implementation of element formulations and boundary conditions. Required level 2 is exceeded; achieved level 3 reflects use of formal documented test cases with quantitative pass/fail thresholds."
