      },
      "rationale": "A systematic mesh convergence study using four mesh densities (element edge lengths 0.8 mm, 0.5 mm, 0.3 mm, 0.2 mm) was performed. Richardson extrapolation confirmed asymptotic convergence; GCI values for all three QoIs are below 2%, satisfying the pre-specified acceptance criterion. The production mesh (0.3 mm) was selected as the converged mesh. Required level 2 is exceeded."
