      },
      "rationale": "All production FEA runs converged to the specified residual tolerance (1e-6) with no load-step failures. Automatic load-stepping was enabled to handle post-yield material nonlinearity. Convergence logs are archived for all 11 model replicates. Required level 2 is met exactly; no additional solver error analysis was deemed necessary given the relatively simple load path."
