      "rationale": "An independent senior analyst reviewed all model inputs, boundary conditions, and post-processing scripts prior to production runs. A structured discrepancy checklist based on ASTM F1717 Section 7 was used; all items were resolved before final submission. Required level 2 (basic review) is exceeded; achieved level 3 reflects the formal independent peer review with documented sign-off."
