      },
      "rationale": "Material properties (E, σ_y, ν) were obtained from certified test reports for the specific Ti-6Al-4V lot used in both FEA and bench testing. Geometric inputs were measured by CMM on five production screws; mean and standard deviation were used to define the Monte Carlo input distributions. The input uncertainty budget is fully documented and traceable to primary measurements. Required level 3 is met."
