        "type": "AcceptanceCriteria",
        "description": "N=11 non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw constructs tested across two independent laboratories (Lab 1: n=6; Lab 2: n=5). All constructs from the same production lot as the FEA material inputs. Sample traceability documented via lot numbers and CMM records. Achieved Gradation 3: multi-laboratory sample set with full traceability."
      },
      "rationale": "The 11-construct sample set spans two independent laboratories, providing inter-laboratory reproducibility data. All constructs are from the same certified production lot as the material property inputs, ensuring consistency between model inputs and test samples. Full traceability is documented via lot numbers, CMM records, and laboratory chain-of-custody logs. Required level 3 is met."
